Package: MBD
Title: Download and Process Movebank Animal Tracking Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Victor", "CAT", email = "victor.cat@ofb.gouv.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A simple package to download animal tracking data from Movebank,
    split by individual, and filter by geographic polygon and taxa. Uses the
    same YAML configuration format for easy setup.
